reviewText: Gave as a gift to my father and he likes it.
I thought I was buying a book

Excellent video with great footage of Rock Island trains and head end power. Includes some steam power, but mostly diesel. Freight, passenger, high speed trains dashing across the countryside... what's not to like?
Extensive coverage of the Rock Island, I really enjoyed it.  This is one of the less-written about roads, so this is a great resource for those seeking information about this unique road.
